author: AETerry
title: Beach Trip Review
review:
I bought this quick, fun and easy to build set for my daughter. Her primary interest was in the little Chihuahua and a few of the accessory pieces. She still enjoyed the rest of the build. For her, bit a little bit older, the build was too simple, especially with the car.

But that's the point of the Junior line, get younger kids into building and seeing they can do it.
